instead of using chicken,
feel free to go with

21:13.998 --> 21:17.016
whatever insect
or small mammal goes well

21:17.018 --> 21:18.776
with Calasparra rice.

21:18.778 --> 21:20.278
Well, that's all
you need to know.

21:20.280 --> 21:22.521
Let me know in the comments
how it turned out,

21:22.523 --> 21:25.157
and what shape
you think the sun is.

